rows.label: qst720303_msg0001
rows.name: Kei!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0002
rows.name: Kai-niichan!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0003
rows.name: D'aww.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0004
rows.name: I can't thank you enough!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0005
rows.name:
Careful you don't lose her again, kid.
You should be looking out for your
little sis, you know!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0006
rows.name:
Yeah... I'll make sure that never
happens again.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0007
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Hikari actually being level-headed.
Never thought I'd see the day...

rows.label: qst720303_msg0008
rows.name:
Hey, Kai-niichan... You left this behind. I've
been holding onto it the whole time.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0009
rows.name: Oh!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0010
rows.name:
I thought that was gone for ever!
Nice one, Kei!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0011
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]It looks just like Laura's mother's
keepsake..

rows.label: qst720303_msg0012
rows.name: Hey...

rows.label: qst720303_msg0013
rows.name: Mind if I take a look at that?

rows.label: qst720303_msg0014
rows.name: No problem!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0015
rows.name: Hmm...

rows.label: qst720303_msg0016
rows.name: How did you come by this?

rows.label: qst720303_msg0017
rows.name: I got it from Auntie Rynea!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0018
rows.name: What?!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0019
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]My mother...

rows.label: qst720303_msg0020
rows.name:
Auntie Rynea had another one, but
Kai-niichan was always hankering after it.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0021
rows.name:
She said it was really precious to her
and she couldn't let it go.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0022
rows.name:
So she made me one that looked a bit
like it.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0023
rows.name:
She said she was sorry she couldn't
make it any better.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0024
rows.name:
I mean, I don't care about that so
much. She made it for me.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0025
rows.name:
So, it's precious to me, no matter what
it looks like.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0026
rows.name:
I see...
Well, take care of yourselves, you two.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0027
rows.name: We promise!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0028
rows.name:
Hey...the way you said that just now...
It sounded just like Auntie Rynea.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0029
rows.name: Yeah, just like her...

rows.label: qst720303_msg0030
rows.name: Haha... I don't doubt it.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0031
rows.name:
I'm sure that we could converse for
hours... But I'd like to propose a course
of action for our new friends here.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0032
rows.name: For us, you mean...?

rows.label: qst720303_msg0033
rows.name:
That's right. Our vessel here will
soon return to Superbia.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0034
rows.name:
Perhaps you two ought to be aboard
when it sets sail.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0035
rows.name:
A wise idea. Things are not so
unsettled in Superbia.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0036
rows.name: Superbia, huh...?

rows.label: qst720303_msg0037
rows.name: No! I made a promise to our da!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0038
rows.name:
He said he was waiting for us...
We can't leave Gula!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0039
rows.name: You're right...

rows.label: qst720303_msg0040
rows.name:
Thanks, but I guess we can't come with
you... We need to stay behind and wait
for Da at the camp.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0041
rows.name:
Understood.
We cannot force you to come.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0042
rows.name:
Indeed... If you start moving around
now, there's a chance you might miss
him.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0043
rows.name:
Of course we'll leave you with some
provisions so you won't get hungry.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0044
rows.name: Yeah, OK. Thank you for everything!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0045
rows.name: I bring news!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0046
rows.name: Something tells me it's urgent...

rows.label: qst720303_msg0047
rows.name: Correct, Ma'am!

rows.label: qst720303_msg0048
rows.name:
If I may, this information is for
His Highness's ears only...

rows.label: qst720303_msg0049
rows.name: You may approach.

rows.label: qst720303_msg0050
rows.name: *whisper* *whisper*

rows.label: qst720303_msg0051
rows.name: I see...

rows.label: qst720303_msg0052
rows.name:
Everyone. May I ask you to reconvene
in the boat's strategy room later?

rows.label: qst720303_msg0053
rows.name: Something unforeseen, is it?

rows.label: qst720303_msg0054
rows.name:
Indeed... I'll give you the
details presently.
